ch.png\" alt=\"TechCrunch logo\" class=\"wp-image-22637\" style=\"width:64px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img width=\"319\" height=\"80\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2023/10/Harvard.png\" alt=\"Harvard logo\" class=\"wp-image-22638\" style=\"width:160px\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/Harvard.png?w=319&amp;ssl=1 319w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/Harvard.png?resize=300%2C75&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 319px) 100vw, 319px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignwide is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/showcase/\">Explore the Showcase</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-default has-charcoal-1-background-color has-background is-vertical is-content-justification-left is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-9 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2660\" height=\"484\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-22644\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png?w=2660&amp;ssl=1 2660w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png?resize=300%2C55&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png?resize=1024%2C186&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png?resize=768%2C140&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png?resize=1536%2C279&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-top-row-full.png?resize=2048%2C373&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2660px) 100vw, 2660px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2640\" height=\"484\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-22641\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png?w=2640&amp;ssl=1 2640w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png?resize=300%2C55&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png?resize=1024%2C188&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png?resize=768%2C141&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png?resize=1536%2C282&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-middle-row.png?resize=2048%2C375&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2640px) 100vw, 2640px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2640\" height=\"384\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-22642\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png?w=2640&amp;ssl=1 2640w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png?resize=300%2C44&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png?resize=1024%2C149&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png?resize=768%2C112&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png?resize=1536%2C223&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/10/showcase-bottom-row.png?resize=2048%2C298&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2640px) 100vw, 2640px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-14 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"community\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:40px;height:60px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer is-style-dots-background\"></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-top:40px;padding-bottom:40px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-charcoal-0-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-05288a29a8d8fcd193b02ae3ae1dfa1a is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-3-font-size\" style=\"margin-top:0\">Meet the WordPress community</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Behind the technology is a diverse collective of people collaborating and gathering from around the world. We hold regular events with opportunities to learn more about WordPress and the latest tech trends, connect with fellow industry experts, and foster your professional growth.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">We’re united by the spirit of open source, and the freedom to build, transform, and share without barriers. Everyone is welcome.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-link-color wp-elements-a228dc12079caf5cdc3dab8774649839\" style=\"margin-top:30px\"><a href=\"https://events.wordpress.org/\">Find an event near you</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1216\" height=\"593\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png\" alt=\"A black and white photograph of excited, applauding attendees in the audience at a WordPress event.\" class=\"wp-image-39810\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?w=1216&amp;ssl=1 1216w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?resize=1024%2C499&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?resize=768%2C375&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1216px) 100vw, 1216px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:5rem\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-charcoal-0-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-58aa10a6f6be213fd2039b905f8f371f is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-inter-font-family\" style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:1.88\"><strong>Build for yourself, not by yourself</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Whether you’re an entrepreneur, professional developer, or first-time blogger, there’s a library of resources and learning tools ready for you. Plus, you have the whole WordPress community in your corner.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-13 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n<p class=\"has-link-color wp-elements-866d66f821ab945f6c09e3baaa5fc688\"><a href=\"https://learn.wordpress.org/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://learn.wordpress.org/\">Learn how to use WordPress</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-link-color wp-elements-b6d0ed985fde1afe834964fdebfb2fcf\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/playground/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://wordpress.org/playground/\">Test WordPress out in your browser</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-link-color wp-elements-53b8135852de48ebeecceb93f2b1200a\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://wordpress.org/documentation/\">Search documentation</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-link-color wp-elements-4f90e910661341867f737331ce55561c\"><a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org\">Dig into the code</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-light-grey-2-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-18 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"news\" style=\"padding-top:5rem;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-content-justification-space-between is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-15 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-3-font-size\">Latest WordPress news</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\">More news</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\"><ul class=\"is-3-column wp-block-wporg-latest-news\"><li><div class=\"wp-block-wporg-latest-news__title\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2025/03/wordpress-6-8-beta-2/\">WordPress 6.8 Beta 2</a></div> <div class=\"wp-block-wporg-latest-news__details\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/category/development/\" class=\"wp-block-wporg-latest-news__category\">Development</a> <span>·</span> <time datetime=\"2025-03-11T15:46:13+00:00\">March 11, 2025</time></div></li><li><div class=\"wp-block-wporg-latest-news__title\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2025/03/wordpress-6-8-beta-1/\">WordPress 6.8 Beta 1</a></div> <div class=\"wp-block-wporg-lat